---
---
<!-- Sanad Keilmuan Section -->
<section id="sanad" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
            <span class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Sanad Bersambung</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary mb-6">Mata Rantai Sanad Keilmuan</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-8">Ilmu agama bersumber dari transmisi guru yang jelas. Kami melestarikan mata rantai silsilah keilmuan yang bersambung hingga Rasulullah SAW.</p>
            
            <!-- Quote on Sanad -->
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-background rounded-2xl p-6 border border-border/50 shadow-inner">
                <p class="font-arabic text-2xl text-primary leading-relaxed mb-3">إِنَّ هَذَا الْعِلْمَ دِينٌ، فَانْظُرُوا عَمَّنْ تَأْخُذُونَ دِينَكُمْ</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted/90 leading-relaxed font-medium">"Sesungguhnya ilmu ini adalah bagian dari agama, maka perhatikanlah dari siapa kalian mengambil agama kalian." (Atsar Shahih Riwayat Imam Muslim, Muqaddimah Shahih Muslim, Bab 5)</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative sanad-line py-8">
            <!-- Timeline Node 1 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center mb-12 reveal">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right text-left pl-16 md:pl-0">
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-primary">Rasulullah SAW</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Sumber utama risalah keilmuan dan wahyu ilahi.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Node 2 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center mb-12 reveal">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-left pl-16">
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-primary">Para Sahabat & Tabi'in</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Menjaga kemurnian syariat dan mengajarkannya turun-temurun.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Node 3 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center mb-12 reveal">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right text-left pl-16 md:pl-0">
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-primary leading-tight">Abuya Sayyid Muhammad bin Alawy Al-Maliki</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Muhaddis terkemuka abad ini dari Makkah Al-Mukarramah.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Node 4 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center mb-12 reveal">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-left pl-16">
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-primary">KH. Muhammad Ihya' Ulumiddin</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Murid langsung Abuya di Makkah, pembawa sanad Makkah ke Indonesia.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Node 5 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center reveal">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right text-left pl-16 md:pl-0">
                    <div class="bg-background p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-premium inline-block md:float-right w-full border border-border/50 text-center md:text-right">
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-primary">Ma'had Nurul Haromain Lin Nisa'</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-2">Menyalurkan ilmu agama, adab keputrian, dan thariqah Ahlussunnah kepada santriwati.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-6 h-6 bg-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white z-10 shadow-md"></div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
